      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ORGANISED CRIME (2) three runs back posted a scintillating 23.42 win over 425m at Bendigo then has found the minor money in two runs since. Hot win three back and looks the one to beat here. CRACK ON (1) last appeared when too good (26.18) over 460m at this track on December 23. Has not been seen since finishing second (26.18) over 460m at this track on December 23. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Will go close here with a clear run. NO EXIT (3) is a talented dog who was quickly into stride and found the front with an all the way win (25.80) at this track in Mix 6/7 over 460m. Fast beginner who should quickly stride to the lead. The form out of his last race has been franked. Should be in this for a long way. BING BING SLAYER (7) placed last time (26.09) at this track in a Mix 6/7, finishing second and beaten 4 lengths. Already a winner from this draw.",
